org.batfish.coordinator.id

Interface IdManager

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IdResolver
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FileBasedIdManager

    @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
public interface IdManager
extends IdResolver
    Reader and writer for persistent mappings between object names and their IDs.
